title: Mylène Farmer: Stade de France (Video 2009)
overview: The Stade de France DVD follows the 2009 tour that was captured during performances at the Stade de France near Paris.
storyline: Grand-scale concert performance of French pop diva Mylène Farmer took place in Paris at the Stade de France stadium. Two final concert tour and 160 thousand people who came to see the show with the present of Hollywood scale special effects and inherent to the French temperament inflame feelings. A huge stage is located on itself tons of light, sound and scenery. The sound of the best songs for more than 25 years of career, accompanied by perfectly choreographed and full of open feeling very secretive French singer. Tears of joy and Mylène Farmer causing a storm of emotions in response of her loving fans.
